{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0609","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1521","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","【核心原理】"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02506","S05-SRC14-A-02507","S05-SRC14-A-02508","S05-SRC14-A-02509"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02524","S05-SRC14-REL-02525","S05-SRC14-REL-02526","S05-SRC14-REL-02527","S05-SRC14-REL-02528","S05-SRC14-REL-02529","S05-SRC14-REL-02530"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2826"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02506","byte_start":186957,"byte_end":187035},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02507","byte_start":187035,"byte_end":187146},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02508","byte_start":187146,"byte_end":187287},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02509","byte_start":187287,"byte_end":187329}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02506","S05-SRC14-A-02507","S05-SRC14-A-02508","S05-SRC14-A-02509"],"core_text":"推断紫微斗数，最看重三方四正，夹宫比较上没那么重要。但推断天相则相反，必须先看夹宫，观察是否能成格局，然后再观察他的三方四正。天相重视夹宫，即是他容易受环境支配的表征，是“两邻相侮”还是“左右逢源”，非常影响天相的特质。十四正曜中，唯天相最重夹宫。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02506","topics":[],"refs":["S06"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02507","topics":[],"refs":["S06"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02508","topics":[],"refs":[],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02509","topics":[],"refs":["S06"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
