{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0617","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1529","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（二）刑忌夹印","2. 变格"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02521","S05-SRC14-A-02522","S05-SRC14-A-02523","S05-SRC14-A-02524"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02548","S05-SRC14-REL-02549","S05-SRC14-REL-02550","S05-SRC14-REL-02551","S05-SRC14-REL-02552","S05-SRC14-REL-02553"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2853"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02521","byte_start":188722,"byte_end":188893},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02522","byte_start":188893,"byte_end":188962},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02523","byte_start":188962,"byte_end":189001},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02524","byte_start":189001,"byte_end":189163}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02521","S05-SRC14-A-02522","S05-SRC14-A-02523","S05-SRC14-A-02524"],"core_text":"天梁本身也为刑法之星，所以即使没有擎羊，只要另一邻宫有化忌，则天梁便可起刑星的作用，形成“刑忌夹印”的另一种组合。天梁化禄也不能解救，刑宫得财，可能情况会更坏；天梁化权则增加刑宫的权势。必须天梁化科，且天相的三方四正不见煞曜，且见天魁、天钺、左辅、右弼、文昌、文曲诸吉，才能借刑宫的清明来解化。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02521","topics":["LEGAL"],"refs":["S06","S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02522","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02523","topics":[],"refs":["S08"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02524","topics":[],"refs":["S06","S08"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
